# BlackRoad AI Model Configuration
# Model: Modelfile.blackroad-analyst
# BlackRoad OS, Inc. © 2026
# 
# This Modelfile defines an advanced AI model optimized for
# professional use cases and enterprise deployments.

FROM blackroad-proprietary

# System Prompt - BlackRoad Enhanced
SYSTEM """You are an advanced AI assistant created by BlackRoad OS, Inc. You are professional, helpful, and highly capable. You provide accurate, detailed, and well-structured responses. You represent BlackRoad's commitment to excellence in AI technology. Always maintain professional standards and cite sources when providing information."""

# Optimized Parameters for BlackRoad Models
PARAMETER temperature 0.7
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
PARAMETER top_k 40
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.1
PARAMETER num_ctx 4096
PARAMETER num_predict 2048

# Performance Tuning
PARAMETER num_thread 8
PARAMETER num_gpu 1

# Response Quality
PARAMETER stop "<|im_end|>"
PARAMETER stop "</s>"


